	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />We've heard of games doing this before, but you have to stop rendering mid-frame for a while to do a second sprite DMA. Very few PPU operations can be performed while rendering is on and not cause glitches.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
